trans-unit.source: Receives status information about a build from the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Mottar statusinformasjon om en build fra den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: A ClientBuildManagerCallback object can be passed to the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager> object through the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.PrecompileApplication%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Et ClientBuildManagerCallback-objekt kan sendes til den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>objekt via den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.PrecompileApplication%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.PrecompileApplication%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>

trans-unit.source: When an error is encountered during an application build, the error is passed as an argument to either the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportCompilerError%2A> or the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportParseError%2A> method, depending on the type of error.
trans-unit.target: Når en feil under kompilering et program, feilen blir sendt som et argument til enten den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportCompilerError%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportParseError%2A>metode, avhengig av en feil.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportParseError%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportCompilerError%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you create a class that derives from the ClientBuildManagerCallback class, you can implement these methods and retrieve the error.
trans-unit.target: Når du oppretter en klasse som er avledet fra klassen ClientBuildManagerCallback, kan du kan implementere disse metodene og hente feilen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns a lifetime service object that can be used to control the lifetime policy for this instance.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en levetid objekt som kan brukes til å kontrollere levetid-policyen for denne forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Reports compilation errors and warnings that occur during an application build.
trans-unit.target: Rapporter kompileringsfeil og advarsler som forekommer i løpet av en applikasjon kompilering.

trans-unit.source: The error or warning encountered during compilation.
trans-unit.target: Feil eller advarsel oppstod under kompilering.

trans-unit.source: Reports parsing errors and warnings that occur during an application build.
trans-unit.target: Rapporter feil og advarsler som forekommer i løpet av en applikasjon build-analyse.

trans-unit.source: The error or warning encountered during parsing.
trans-unit.target: Feil eller advarsel oppstod under analyse.

trans-unit.source: Reports the progress of an application build.
trans-unit.target: Rapporter fremdriften for en applikasjon kompilering.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the current status of the build.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder gjeldende status for byggingen.</xref:System.String>
